    diagonal comparison `invDiagBound j <= ‖A_jj‖`. -/
theorem higham13_algorithm13_3_clm_initial_diag_bound_of_diag_inverse
    {m : ℕ} {E : Type*}
    [NormedAddCommGroup E] [NormedSpace ℝ E] [ProperSpace E]
    (hunit : ({x : E | ‖x‖ = 1} : Set E).Nonempty)
