  refine ⟨L, U, ?_, ?_⟩
  · simpa [L, U] using
      higham13_algorithm13_3_matrixStages_blockLUFactSpec_of_product_eq
        A pivotInv hprod
  · simpa [L, U] using
      higham13_algorithm13_3_matrixStages_LU_product_bound
        hm hr A pivotInv hId hLower hUpper

