                (m + 1) hkm) *
            ⅟(blockMatrixFirstSplitA11
                (higham13_algorithm13_3_activeSuffixStageTailBlock A pivotInv k
                  (m + 1) hkm)) *
              blockMatrixFirstSplitA12
                (higham13_algorithm13_3_activeSuffixStageTailBlock A pivotInv k
